# Bimarz VPN Landing Page - Project Structure & Overview

## Project Context
This is a **Next.js 14** landing page featuring a **Typography Emotion Journey** across 7 pages. The project tells a story from fear and surveillance to freedom and joy, perfect for the Bimarz VPN service.

## Key Files & Architecture

### Main Entry Points
- [app/page.tsx](mdc:app/page.tsx) - Main page with navigation logic and page switching
- [app/layout.tsx](mdc:app/layout.tsx) - Root layout with ThemeProvider
- [app/globals.css](mdc:app/globals.css) - Global styles, CSS variables, and theme system

### Component Structure
- **Individual Pages**: [components/pages/](mdc:components/pages/) contains Page1-Page7, each with unique animations
- **Layout Components**: 
  - [components/Header.tsx](mdc:components/Header.tsx) - Header with logo, navigation, language switcher, theme toggle
  - [components/Footer.tsx](mdc:components/Footer.tsx) - Footer with links and social icons
  - [components/PageIndicator.tsx](mdc:components/PageIndicator.tsx) - Vertical page indicator (right side)
  - [components/ScrollIndicator.tsx](mdc:components/ScrollIndicator.tsx) - Animated scroll hint
- **Reusable Components**: 
  - [components/GlassCard.tsx](mdc:components/GlassCard.tsx) - Glass morphism component
  - [components/ThemeRipple.tsx](mdc:components/ThemeRipple.tsx) - Theme transition effect

### State Management
- [contexts/ThemeContext.tsx](mdc:contexts/ThemeContext.tsx) - Theme and language state management
- [lib/translations.ts](mdc:lib/translations.ts) - Multi-language support (6 languages)

### Configuration Files
- [package.json](mdc:package.json) - Dependencies: Next.js 14, React 18, Framer Motion, TypeScript
- [tailwind.config.ts](mdc:tailwind.config.ts) - Tailwind configuration with custom animations
- [tsconfig.json](mdc:tsconfig.json) - TypeScript strict mode configuration

## The 7-Page Journey

1. **Page1 (EXPOSED)** - Fear & Danger with red glitch effects
2. **Page2 (YOU)** - Surveillance with circular scanning animation
3. **Page3 (BLOCKED)** - Frustration with censor bars
4. **Page4 (?)** - Hope with emerging warm light
5. **Page5 (VPN SOLUTION)** - Confidence with aurora waves
6. **Page6 (OPEN SOURCE)** - Trust with glass cathedral and VPN icons
7. **Page7 (FREE!)** - Joy & Freedom with celebration and pricing

## Key Features

- **Navigation**: Pages 1-6 use scroll/swipe to switch pages; Page 7 has normal scrolling
- **Themes**: Light/Dark modes with ripple transition effect
- **Languages**: English, Farsi, Chinese, Russian, Ukrainian, Hindi
- **Responsive**: Mobile-first design with proper spacing
- **Animations**: Unique animation per page using Framer Motion

## Design Principles

- **Spacing**: 80-100px margins from header/footer, 24px minimum between elements
- **No Overlaps**: Content never overlaps at any screen size
- **Professional Colors**: No ugly or overly saturated colors
- **Typography**: Lalezar font with responsive scaling
- **Performance**: GPU-accelerated animations, 60fps smooth

